{
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "text": "%md\n\n# Employee EDA from HDFS\n\nThis notebook demonstrates Exploratory Data Analysis on employee data stored in HDFS.\n\n## Objectives\n- Load CSV data from HDFS using PySpark\n- Perform data quality checks\n- Compute statistics and distributions\n- Visualize insights\n- Answer: \"Do salaries vary by sector?\"\n\n---",
      "user": "anonymous",
      "dateUpdated": "2026-03-19T00:00:00+0000",
      "progress": 0,
      "config": {
        "tableHide": false,
        "editorSetting": {
          "language": "markdown",
          "editOnDblClick": true
        },
        "colWidth": 12,
        "editorMode": "ace/mode/markdown",
